Interface PropertyMethod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotatedElement<Method>, AnnotatedMethod
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPropertyMethod, GetPropertyMethod, SetPropertyMethod

    public interface PropertyMethod
extends AnnotatedMethod
    Defines the interface for property accessor methods (i.e. get/is/set methods).
